{"title":"公社麦收","authors":["吴大宇"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":6,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社麦收"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四川开县向穴人民公社　吴大宇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开镰曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南风吹，麦子黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片金色染山岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社出动突击队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红战旗十里扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车车麦把上晒场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀飞舞闪银光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声起处金波滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收暖进人心房。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晒麦场上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社晒麦场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦堆顶太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奶奶看场场边坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙孙山下捉迷藏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦山一座连一座，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜煞老小一满堂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奶拉孙孙来谈心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙孙巧说馍馍香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指挥田中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦穗沙沙似铃摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记割麦不弯腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半天才收一个角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急得热汗遍身浇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员纷纷来助战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争谈丰收笑语高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘吵镰不耐用，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙嚷着换新刀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运麦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牲蹄飞翻尘土扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村道上面车成行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头接麦田尾齐坝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金山车上装！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一曲“丰收谣”没唱完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万座金山卸晒场！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐得队长大声嚷："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“快快修新仓！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷声紧，春雨急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯海沸腾人马密。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴风雨要抢走粮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员不许争穗粒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银镰落，歌声起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抢收人儿喜喜雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"?牛挥鞭把田犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千顷绿秧插田里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编围席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓郁麦香扑院门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬老院中喜气生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷婆婆脸堆笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"院坝编席手不停。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"围席节节朝前伸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社麦囤顶云层，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜歌上口嘴角流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收忙坏编席人！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}